gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.model

Class ConstantTerm

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.model.ModelTerm
      • gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.model.ConstantTerm

  • @Embeddable
public final class ConstantTerm
extends ModelTerm

    A constant term. Simply adds a constant to a risk model. (Each risk model will have one, and only one, of these.)

    Per Effective Java Item 17, this class is marked final because it was not designed for inheritance.
